<%- include("background.ejs") %>

<style>
    /* --- CSS Changes Summary ---
    1. Changed .support-highlight colors to earthy tones to match original Pauri theme.
    2. Changed .support-highlight p and span to use strong tags (or just rely on the content being bolded).
    3. Updated related theme colors (kits-list h3, call-to-action .hashtags) to a cohesive deep forest green (#1f3d05).
    */

    body {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #333;
    }

    /* Green/Earth tones for HP Hero */
    .hp-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7), rgba(47, 69, 7, 0.7)), url('https://placehold.co/1500x500/8B9A7A/8B9A7A') no-repeat center center/cover;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .hp-hero h1 {
        font-size: 3.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hp-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .intro-section p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #555;
    }

    /* REVISED COLOR SCHEME for highlight box: Earthy Green */
    .support-highlight {
        background-color: #e8f5e9; /* Lightest green */
        border-left: 5px solid #2f4507; /* Deep forest green border */
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 40px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .support-highlight p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        color: #2f4507; /* Deep forest green text */
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .support-highlight span {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .kits-list {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .kits-list h3 {
        color: #1f3d05; /* Deep forest green */
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.8em;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .kits-list ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .kits-list li {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .kits-list li::before {
        content: 'ðŸ©¹'; 
        margin-right: 15px;
        font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    .gallery-section h3 {
        color: #1f3d05; /* Deep forest green */
        font-size: 2.2em;
        margin-top: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .gallery-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .gallery-item img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .gallery-item img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    
    .call-to-action {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 50px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .call-to-action p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .call-to-action .hashtags {
        color: #2f4507; /* Deep forest green for hashtags */
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>

<div class="hp-hero">
    <h1>FLASHFLOOD RELIEF: KULLU & MANALI</h1>
</div>

<div class="hp-container">
    <div class="intro-section">
        <p>The monsoon season brought a series of devastating cloudbursts across Himachal Pradesh, with Mandi and Kullu districts being severely affected by flashfloods.</p>
        <p>Mountain Forum Himalayas (MFH) quickly mobilized support for the survivor families in **Manali and Kullu blocks.**</p>
    </div>

    <div class="support-highlight">
        <p>This joint relief effort, supported by <span>Amazon and Donatekart</span>, provided critical aid to <span>250 Flashflood survivor families</span> across <span>15 villages</span>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="kits-list">
        <h3>Items Distributed to Help Families Recover:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Shelter Kits (Tarpaulins, Blankets)</li>
            <li>Hygiene Kits (Soaps, Sanitary items, Detergents)</li>
            <li>Dry Ration Packs (Rice, Pulses, Oil, Salt)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="gallery-section">
        <h3>Distribution Highlights from Himachal Pradesh</h3>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="himachal.jpg" alt="Relief Distribution in Kullu Block">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="hima.jpg" alt="Volunteers and Panchayat members during distribution">
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="hima3.jpg" alt="Flashflood survivor receiving kit">
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic; color: #777;">Distribution was carried out with the help of local volunteers and panchayats to ensure maximum reach in 5 villages of Naggar and 10 villages of Kullu block.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="call-to-action">
        <p>Strong community support and cooperation are vital for recovery. Thank you to all partners!</p>
        <p class="hashtags">#HimachalFloods #KulluManaliRelief #MFHSupport #AmazonDonatekart</p>
    </div>

</div>

